data.description: See the Cinematic Video! Discover the magic of this remarkable Sierra foothill residence! Nestled above the valley fog and below the snow line, this custom-built single-story home offers a year-round outdoor oasis with captivating views and breathtaking sunsets. The backyard is an entertainer's dream, featuring a spacious covered patio, a stunning Cabo-style pool, and a well-appointed outdoor kitchen with ample seating. This .73-acre lot is thoughtfully landscaped for low maintenance and the backyard is fully enclosed, creating a private sanctuary surrounded by native oaks and striking natural rock formations. Inside, a warm and inviting ambiance awaits, with custom barn door sliders gracing the home's interior. The kitchen is a chef's delight, boasting custom cabinets, exquisite granite countertops, tile backsplash,  hammered metal farm sink, gas cooktop, and a versatile island with pendant lighting. Additional highlights include owned solar with Tesla charger, whole-house fan, and a generously sized upstairs bonus room, offering flexibility for a home office, workout space, or more. This move-in-ready sanctuary of beauty and tranquility is located in Auburn Valley, a private community where a desirable lifestyle and a strong sense of community thrive!
